1
00:00:19,708 --> 00:00:20,832
[Previously]
Put down those straw sandals!

2
00:00:21,125 --> 00:00:22,125
Fine.

3
00:00:22,167 --> 00:00:23,167
Get on your knees and beg me!

4
00:00:24,625 --> 00:00:26,457
Rotten wood cannot be carved.

5
00:00:26,625 --> 00:00:28,082
That phrase suits you barbarians

6
00:00:28,667 --> 00:00:29,874
from Great Li perfectly.

7
00:00:30,333 --> 00:00:31,333
For scum like you,

8
00:00:31,708 --> 00:00:32,708
fists are the only language

9
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:34,916
Once you're lying on the ground,

10
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,499
we'll see if you still want to talk reason.

11
00:00:37,042 --> 00:00:38,249
Who gave you the guts

12
00:00:38,542 --> 00:00:40,374
to bully my disciples?

13
00:00:40,708 --> 00:00:41,708
Shut your mouth,

14
00:00:41,792 --> 00:00:42,832
you insolent brat!

15
00:00:43,083 --> 00:00:44,791
Today, I'll teach you a lesson

16
00:00:44,792 --> 00:00:46,666
you ungrateful grandson!

17
00:00:48,042 --> 00:00:49,416
Bullied my son like that?

18
00:00:50,083 --> 00:00:51,249
Screw your mother's Great Sui!

19
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:57,043
[I want a real challenger! - Parents in this world are heroes themselves]
Episode 18
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

20
00:00:59,583 --> 00:01:00,583
[Door slams open]

21
00:01:00,583 --> 00:01:01,249
Mister Qi,

22
00:01:01,250 --> 00:01:02,499
I know the rules.

23
00:01:02,708 --> 00:01:04,999
That wench clawed my wife's face bloody,

24
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,332
and I couldn't swallow that humiliation.

25
00:01:06,792 --> 00:01:08,707
So I went and cursed out her ancestors,

26
00:01:08,917 --> 00:01:10,707
and tore down their Ancestral Hall.

27
00:01:10,833 --> 00:01:12,666
I haven't said a word about it since.

28
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:13,916
Relax.

29
00:01:14,167 --> 00:01:15,707
I'm not here to call you to account.

30
00:01:15,958 --> 00:01:16,958
I'm here to drink.

31
00:01:18,503 --> 00:01:19,010
Dad,

32
00:01:19,417 --> 00:01:20,417
I'm full.

33
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:24,833
This wine is terrible.

34
00:01:25,250 --> 00:01:26,874
Forgive me, Mister Qi.

35
00:01:28,417 --> 00:01:29,417
It's good.

36
00:01:29,833 --> 00:01:30,791
Back in my youth,

37
00:01:30,833 --> 00:01:32,166
I used to drink swill like this often.

38
00:01:32,542 --> 00:01:33,332
And my temper back then

39
00:01:33,333 --> 00:01:34,416
was far worse than yours.

40
00:01:39,750 --> 00:01:40,874
Over at the Academy,

41
00:01:41,542 --> 00:01:42,624
there's still no movement.

42
00:01:43,542 --> 00:01:44,541
Old Man Mao only said

43
00:01:45,125 --> 00:01:46,457
he would give His Majesty an explanation.

44
00:01:47,208 --> 00:01:48,208
He didn't mention

45
00:01:48,458 --> 00:01:49,541
when he'd enter the palace.

46
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,874
If Old Man Mao won't come,

47
00:01:54,250 --> 00:01:55,999
I can't exactly pressure the Academy

48
00:01:56,125 --> 00:01:57,457
into serving justice, can I?

49
00:01:59,417 --> 00:02:00,832
This "Turning Page Gale"

50
00:02:01,042 --> 00:02:02,249
is a guest hard to invite.

51
00:02:08,292 --> 00:02:10,041
Where is the Emperor of Great Sui?

52
00:02:13,417 --> 00:02:15,082
Just how strong is this guy?

53
00:02:15,833 --> 00:02:17,332
He's so audacious,

54
00:02:18,167 --> 00:02:20,457
yet he's merely a formidable
Ninth-Rank Martial Artist.

55
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,041
Allow me to test him.

56
00:02:22,708 --> 00:02:23,041
Agreed.

57
00:02:23,042 --> 00:02:23,874
If I lose,

58
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:25,041
Your Majesty

59
00:02:25,042 --> 00:02:26,207
can simply show yourself.

60
00:02:27,833 --> 00:02:29,249
Just don't make it too ugly.

61
00:02:30,958 --> 00:02:32,166
Unless absolutely necessary,

62
00:02:32,583 --> 00:02:35,582
I won't borrow the Imperial Dragon Qi
of the capital.

63
00:02:41,833 --> 00:02:44,749
I failed to gauge your depth back then.

64
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,124
Exchange three punches.

65
00:02:47,458 --> 00:02:48,541
If you win,

66
00:02:48,833 --> 00:02:50,916
you may meet our Emperor.

67
00:02:52,792 --> 00:02:54,999
I'll let you strike first with two blows.

68
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:57,750
Good.

69
00:03:33,333 --> 00:03:34,624
You have one punch left.

70
00:03:34,917 --> 00:03:36,041
Don't hold back.

71
00:03:36,792 --> 00:03:37,792
However...

72
00:03:38,042 --> 00:03:39,457
I will also make my move.

73
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,791
All soldiers, fall back to the gate!

74
00:03:44,333 --> 00:03:45,874
A Grandmaster with great courage!

75
00:03:46,083 --> 00:03:47,083
Let's continue.

76
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:51,916
Please, teach me.

77
00:04:16,625 --> 00:04:17,625
Hold on.

78
00:04:17,667 --> 00:04:19,207
Rice must be eaten one bite at a time.

79
00:04:19,583 --> 00:04:20,624
Compared to Song Changjing,

80
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,000
this whetstone of yours

81
00:04:22,167 --> 00:04:23,332
isn't heavy enough.

82
00:04:33,542 --> 00:04:35,416
Still refusing to call your master out?

83
00:04:51,458 --> 00:04:52,499
Emperor of Great Sai,

84
00:04:52,583 --> 00:04:53,874
either keep hiding,

85
00:04:54,083 --> 00:04:55,749
send someone stronger,

86
00:04:55,917 --> 00:04:57,124
or if you can't manage that,

87
00:04:57,500 --> 00:04:59,749
have everyone come at me at once.

88
00:05:02,625 --> 00:05:04,041
Be careful.

89
00:05:06,458 --> 00:05:07,666
Your Majesty, rest assured.

90
00:05:12,708 --> 00:05:14,999
Activate the Dragon Wall Formation!

91
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:01,333
Damn it.

92
00:06:01,667 --> 00:06:03,041
I've been suppressed to the Eighth Realm.

93
00:06:03,958 --> 00:06:05,957
It seems that within this
city defense array,

94
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:07,791
all Qi Practitioners and Martial Artists

95
00:06:07,875 --> 00:06:09,374
will be suppressed by the Gao family's
Dragon Qi,

96
00:06:09,833 --> 00:06:11,207
dropping one or two realms.

97
00:06:13,625 --> 00:06:14,625
No matter.

98
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:16,250
Dear grandson,

99
00:06:16,458 --> 00:06:18,082
your ancestor still has many
novel treasures.

100
00:06:18,667 --> 00:06:20,832
Don't die too easily on me.

101
00:06:27,083 --> 00:06:28,457
Using a formation

102
00:06:28,833 --> 00:06:30,249
to suppress me to the Eighth Realm,

103
00:06:33,292 --> 00:06:34,957
to elevate his cultivation.

104
00:06:35,542 --> 00:06:37,332
Though it's only a single realm apart,

105
00:06:37,917 --> 00:06:40,207
the price Great Sui's capital has to pay

106
00:06:40,458 --> 00:06:41,874
is significantly less.

107
00:06:42,125 --> 00:06:44,207
You wish to seek an audience
with our liege?

108
00:06:44,292 --> 00:06:45,292
Fine.

109
00:06:46,542 --> 00:06:49,332
But you should never have been
so arrogant about it.

110
00:06:49,542 --> 00:06:51,374
After all, the Great Sai Court

111
00:06:51,708 --> 00:06:53,457
must maintain its dignity.

112
00:06:57,375 --> 00:06:59,541
Are you saying that the fists of
a Ninth-Rank Martial Artist

113
00:06:59,833 --> 00:07:02,082
cannot match the "face" of your Great Sai?

114
00:07:02,917 --> 00:07:04,624
That is precisely correct.

115
00:07:06,167 --> 00:07:07,707
Anyone who steps out
of the Wuying Hall Plaza

116
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:08,416
and loses...

117
00:07:08,667 --> 00:07:09,667
Well then.

118
00:07:10,208 --> 00:07:11,208
Good fist.

119
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:12,250
Again.

120
00:07:17,125 --> 00:07:18,957
Your Li Er's fists may shatter walls,

121
00:07:19,125 --> 00:07:20,916
but they won't break the rules
of my Great Sai.

122
00:07:21,417 --> 00:07:23,791
If you want to see our Emperor,
crawl out

123
00:07:24,458 --> 00:07:25,666
and then crawl back in

124
00:07:25,708 --> 00:07:26,708
to pay homage.

125
00:07:31,875 --> 00:07:33,207
A mere Ninth-Rank Martial Artist

126
00:07:33,458 --> 00:07:35,624
dares to run wild and cause havoc
in my Great Sai?

127
00:07:36,042 --> 00:07:37,124
Dream on.

128
00:07:39,042 --> 00:07:40,042
Relax.

129
00:07:40,208 --> 00:07:41,791
I'll take good care of myself.

130
00:07:59,250 --> 00:08:00,624
What a true Grandmaster.

131
00:08:01,042 --> 00:08:02,832
Surrounded by tigers and wolves,

132
00:08:02,958 --> 00:08:04,499
yet he remains utterly unreasonable.

133
00:08:04,583 --> 00:08:06,582
My boy is so sensible, yet he gets bullied.

134
00:08:06,708 --> 00:08:08,582
It's all because I, his father,
lack ability.

135
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:10,791
If the Emperor of Great Sai won't see me,

136
00:08:10,958 --> 00:08:12,082
then I'll smash his entire

137
00:08:12,125 --> 00:08:13,125
Great Sai to pieces.

138
00:08:14,375 --> 00:08:15,166
How could he...

139
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:16,707
return to the Ninth Realm?

140
00:08:18,417 --> 00:08:20,832
I only seek justice from
the Emperor of Great Sai.

141
00:08:21,708 --> 00:08:23,041
No matter how hard your fists are,

142
00:08:23,292 --> 00:08:25,207
you cannot break the sky of my Great Sai.

143
00:08:26,208 --> 00:08:28,499
I'll show you what "Dynasty's Face"
truly means.

144
00:08:28,833 --> 00:08:30,874
I'll show you the Thunderbolt
of the Dynasty!

145
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:36,666
Emperor of Great Sai,

146
00:08:36,958 --> 00:08:39,041
it really isn't easy to see you.

147
00:08:41,667 --> 00:08:43,249
This grand formation is probably...

148
00:08:43,708 --> 00:08:44,249
Old Man Mao,

149
00:08:44,375 --> 00:08:45,416
you've finally arrived!

150
00:08:45,917 --> 00:08:47,082
I have some words in my heart

151
00:08:47,417 --> 00:08:48,417
that I must spit out.

152
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:50,416
But I'm clumsy with words
and can't explain it clearly.

153
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,624
Then fight it out clearly.

154
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,666
How dare you be so impudent!

155
00:09:04,875 --> 00:09:05,541
Relax.

156
00:09:05,792 --> 00:09:07,457
I'm not here to call you to account.

157
00:09:07,708 --> 00:09:08,749
I'm here to drink.

158
00:09:12,208 --> 00:09:14,249
You remind me of a brother,
a friend of mine.

159
00:09:14,458 --> 00:09:15,458
He was very much like you.

160
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,249
A strong man draws his blade
against the stronger.

161
00:09:20,792 --> 00:09:21,792
I have no blade.

162
00:09:23,458 --> 00:09:25,041
So a strong man throws a punch

163
00:09:25,042 --> 00:09:26,042
at the even stronger.

164
00:09:27,917 --> 00:09:30,291
If Ninth Realm strength can't
force your submission,

165
00:09:30,875 --> 00:09:32,624
then screw the Ninth Realm—
I'll break through it.

166
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,874
Ninth Realm peak...

167
00:09:35,167 --> 00:09:36,957
Li Er breaks through the realm,

168
00:09:37,292 --> 00:09:39,207
not amidst life and death,

169
00:09:39,375 --> 00:09:40,957
but with a fist aimed higher,

170
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:42,999
releasing a breath from the heart.

171
00:09:51,625 --> 00:09:53,291
All of you, get out of my way!

172
00:10:14,417 --> 00:10:15,417
Good, good.

173
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,416
So Mister Qi saw through it long ago.

174
00:10:22,708 --> 00:10:23,916
The path I, Li Er, have always walked,

175
00:10:23,917 --> 00:10:26,041
yet never realized myself—it was correct.

176
00:10:26,375 --> 00:10:28,082
The feeling of the Tenth Realm is sublime.

177
00:10:28,375 --> 00:10:30,166
Compared to eating chicken legs
left by my son,

178
00:10:30,333 --> 00:10:31,707
the taste is certainly superior.

179
00:10:31,958 --> 00:10:32,958
Rest assured,

180
00:10:33,208 --> 00:10:35,957
I dare not claim to teach Li Huai
much scholarly knowledge,

181
00:10:36,125 --> 00:10:37,874
but I guarantee he will be a good man.

182
00:10:38,083 --> 00:10:39,916
His temperament won't be inferior
to his father's.

183
00:10:40,125 --> 00:10:41,125
Mister Qi,

184
00:10:41,667 --> 00:10:42,667
that is enough.

185
00:10:45,333 --> 00:10:47,791
If I could just drink with Mister Qi again,

186
00:10:48,250 --> 00:10:48,707
then...

187
00:10:48,833 --> 00:10:49,874
that would be even better.

188
00:10:53,458 --> 00:10:54,499
Emperor of Great Sai,

189
00:10:54,833 --> 00:10:55,832
if you don't come out now,

190
00:10:55,833 --> 00:10:56,957
don't bother coming out at all.

191
00:11:07,833 --> 00:11:09,874
You little bastard, are you finally stepping in?

192
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,124
Ancestor, I'll discipline you
some other day, you turtle grandson!

193
00:11:13,375 --> 00:11:14,041
Bah!

194
00:11:15,042 --> 00:11:16,999
The fist of a fiery Martial Artist

195
00:11:17,333 --> 00:11:18,707
is truly extraordinary.

196
00:11:19,917 --> 00:11:22,707
I am the Vice-Principal
of Cliffside Academy,

197
00:11:22,917 --> 00:11:23,999
Mao Xiaodong.

198
00:11:24,375 --> 00:11:25,166
I am here specifically

199
00:11:25,167 --> 00:11:26,582
regarding the matter of Li Huai.

200
00:11:28,917 --> 00:11:30,124
Are you willing to follow me

201
00:11:30,208 --> 00:11:31,791
to meet with His Majesty?

202
00:11:34,667 --> 00:11:36,707
But we'll have to fight one more bout
before that.

203
00:11:37,583 --> 00:11:40,041
If Great Sai believes it stands on the side of reason,

204
00:11:40,042 --> 00:11:41,541
then let's continue fighting.

205
00:11:41,708 --> 00:11:43,416
I know Great Sai has deep pockets

206
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:44,374
..and can withstand the hardships of life."

207
00:11:45,333 --> 00:11:46,749
But I, Li Er, find it bizarre.

208
00:11:47,083 --> 00:11:49,457
If all the officials in Great Sai are
such useless trash,

209
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:52,249
what kind of scholar will my son Li Huai become

210
00:11:52,917 --> 00:11:54,041
studying in a place like this?

211
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:56,332
Do those noble families need to

212
00:11:56,333 --> 00:11:57,916
publicly apologize to Li Huai?

213
00:11:58,375 --> 00:12:00,332
A group of high-ranking lords
apologizing to a child—

214
00:12:00,333 --> 00:12:01,582
how does that even work?

215
00:12:01,917 --> 00:12:03,291
And I don't want my son

216
00:12:03,292 --> 00:12:05,666
unable to study in peace
at Cliffside Academy.

217
00:12:05,792 --> 00:12:06,499
Mister Li Er,

218
00:12:06,667 --> 00:12:07,457
you are indeed reasonable.

219
00:12:07,667 --> 00:12:09,582
I should have met with you sooner.

220
00:12:11,125 --> 00:12:12,582
I am no "Mister."

221
00:12:12,917 --> 00:12:16,207
Old Man Mao and the tutors teaching
Li Huai at the academy are the real deal.

222
00:12:16,792 --> 00:12:17,916
I'll wait right here.

223
00:12:18,333 --> 00:12:20,332
Your Majesty better not try
to stall me deliberately.

224
00:12:21,667 --> 00:12:22,374
I...

225
00:12:22,667 --> 00:12:24,041
I will send someone to deliver the message now.

226
00:12:26,042 --> 00:12:26,791
Old Man Mao,

227
00:12:26,917 --> 00:12:27,917
what advice do you have for me?

228
00:12:29,208 --> 00:12:30,249
It's simple.

229
00:12:30,375 --> 00:12:32,957
Have the members of those families
enter the palace

230
00:12:33,292 --> 00:12:35,541
and bow their heads to Li Er in apology.

231
00:12:36,958 --> 00:12:37,958
Old Man Mao,

232
00:12:38,625 --> 00:12:39,625
tell me the truth.

233
00:12:39,875 --> 00:12:42,166
Were you just waiting for today
to watch me make a fool of myself?

234
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,041
To be honest,

235
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:46,499
even I didn't know

236
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,166
Li Huai had such a father.

237
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,416
Had I known earlier,

238
00:12:49,625 --> 00:12:51,999
I would have entered the palace
to see the Emperor sooner.

239
00:12:52,417 --> 00:12:54,666
Why would things have escalated
to this point?

240
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,166
I am not that muddle-headed.

241
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,749
That Li Er was willing to stop at this point—

242
00:13:00,667 --> 00:13:02,041
Old Man Mao, your contribution is immense.

243
00:13:02,542 --> 00:13:03,542
I...

244
00:13:03,583 --> 00:13:04,874
will order the Ministry of Rites
to commend you.

245
00:13:05,042 --> 00:13:05,624
Unnecessary.

246
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,000
Why?

247
00:13:07,292 --> 00:13:10,207
The way of the gentleman lies
in regulating profit by righteousness,

248
00:13:10,333 --> 00:13:11,457
and controlling material desires
with the heart.

249
00:13:11,625 --> 00:13:12,916
Extensively learn,

250
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,082
inquire accurately,

251
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:15,291
reflect carefully,

252
00:13:15,292 --> 00:13:16,332
discriminate clearly,

253
00:13:16,375 --> 00:13:17,375
and practice earnestly.

254
00:13:18,250 --> 00:13:19,499
Sincerity means

255
00:13:19,708 --> 00:13:22,457
choosing what is good
and holding fast to it.

256
00:13:22,625 --> 00:13:24,291
This is precisely what our

257
00:13:24,417 --> 00:13:26,207
Cliffside Academy embodies.

258
00:13:26,250 --> 00:13:28,041
For the next decades or centuries,

259
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,499
Cliffside Academy

260
00:13:29,708 --> 00:13:30,332
will continue to teach this way,

261
00:13:30,333 --> 00:13:31,957
imparting the Dao and instructing disciples.

262
00:13:32,083 --> 00:13:33,416
We will nurture scholars

263
00:13:33,875 --> 00:13:34,957
for Great Sai,

264
00:13:35,042 --> 00:13:38,416
protecting and cultivating true seeds
of learning.

265
00:13:40,125 --> 00:13:41,125
I...

266
00:13:41,167 --> 00:13:42,374
on behalf of Great Sai's state,

267
00:13:42,875 --> 00:13:44,957
thank Cliffside Academy in advance.

268
00:13:46,208 --> 00:13:47,374
Mao Xiaodong

269
00:13:47,708 --> 00:13:49,291
accepts this for Cliffside Academy

270
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,332
with a clear conscience.

271
00:13:55,542 --> 00:13:56,499
Elder Li Huai,

272
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:57,291
we were wrong.

273
00:13:57,292 --> 00:13:58,332
We were truly wrong.

274
00:13:58,750 --> 00:14:00,541
Master Mao has already punished them,

275
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:02,166
and sent them here specifically
to apologize.

276
00:14:03,708 --> 00:14:04,708
They bullied people like that,

277
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:06,207
and a single apology
makes it water under the bridge?

278
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:07,582
We really were wrong.

279
00:14:07,583 --> 00:14:08,374
If you err and don't change,

280
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,500
what good is that?

281
00:14:13,583 --> 00:14:15,374
I won't let you bully me again.

282
00:14:17,125 --> 00:14:17,999
Where are you going?

283
00:14:18,042 --> 00:14:19,124
Keep kneeling.

284
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:21,957
At home, Mother protects me.

285
00:14:22,083 --> 00:14:24,332
Outside, Chen Ping'an and the others
protect me.

286
00:14:24,667 --> 00:14:25,582
Yet I seem to be

287
00:14:25,667 --> 00:14:27,249
constantly causing trouble for others.

288
00:14:27,667 --> 00:14:29,082
They get hurt because of me...

289
00:14:29,083 --> 00:14:30,832
and it hurts more than if I
were wronged myself.

290
00:14:31,083 --> 00:14:33,791
Why is my courage so lacking?

291
00:14:36,958 --> 00:14:38,707
I have no grudge against you.

292
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,207
You broke in here—

293
00:14:40,292 --> 00:14:41,624
what business brings you?

294
00:14:42,583 --> 00:14:44,332
Damn it, another madman.

295
00:14:45,208 --> 00:14:46,208
Halt.

296
00:14:46,250 --> 00:14:47,457
A "Stopping" Realm Martial Artist.

297
00:14:47,542 --> 00:14:48,291
You... are...

298
00:14:48,542 --> 00:14:50,041
Cai Jingshen,

299
00:14:50,875 --> 00:14:51,875
correct?

300
00:14:54,125 --> 00:14:54,666
No.

301
00:14:54,667 --> 00:14:55,667
I am not.

302
00:15:00,917 --> 00:15:01,917
You...

303
00:15:08,333 --> 00:15:08,749
If you have the skill,

304
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:09,541
if you have the guts,

305
00:15:09,708 --> 00:15:11,541
come fight me again!

306
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:16,666
I'm talking to that young man in white
from the other day.

307
00:15:17,625 --> 00:15:18,625
You?

308
00:15:18,792 --> 00:15:20,499
You're not involved.

309
00:15:23,375 --> 00:15:23,707
Mother,

310
00:15:24,083 --> 00:15:24,541
Sister,

311
00:15:24,833 --> 00:15:26,082
I missed you guys.

312
00:15:26,458 --> 00:15:27,082
Son!

313
00:15:27,333 --> 00:15:28,333
My boy!

314
00:15:32,167 --> 00:15:32,707
Dad,

315
00:15:32,708 --> 00:15:33,332
Mother...

316
00:15:33,542 --> 00:15:35,374
What are you doing here?

317
00:15:41,375 --> 00:15:42,916
My Huai'zi has gotten thin.

318
00:15:43,125 --> 00:15:44,874
Mother's heart is breaking.

319
00:15:46,458 --> 00:15:47,458
Alright, alright.

320
00:15:49,292 --> 00:15:50,416
I'm doing great, really.

321
00:15:50,708 --> 00:15:52,291
I have so many wonderful things too.

322
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:53,874
Come,

323
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,041
let me show you.

324
00:16:01,833 --> 00:16:02,666
Let's go.

325
00:16:03,375 --> 00:16:04,375
Slow down.

326
00:16:09,375 --> 00:16:10,999
Monstrous talents appear every year,

327
00:16:11,583 --> 00:16:12,957
but this year there's an especially
large crop.

328
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,082
What do you think?

329
00:16:16,458 --> 00:16:18,124
It was made for me by Chen Ping'an.

330
00:16:18,208 --> 00:16:19,208
Isn't it pretty?

331
00:16:19,250 --> 00:16:20,916
Aren't you jealous?

332
00:16:21,750 --> 00:16:22,916
Good.

333
00:16:23,375 --> 00:16:24,375
Truly good.

334
00:16:24,667 --> 00:16:25,082
Also...

335
00:16:25,167 --> 00:16:25,749
this one.

336
00:16:27,875 --> 00:16:28,875
On the journey here,

337
00:16:29,292 --> 00:16:30,499
did anyone bully you?

338
00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:33,458
No.

339
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,041
Chen Ping'an protected us.

340
00:16:35,208 --> 00:16:36,291
He is such a good person.

341
00:16:36,583 --> 00:16:38,207
He gave us all the best things.

342
00:16:38,542 --> 00:16:40,374
It's a pity Li Liu isn't good enough
for him.

343
00:16:43,292 --> 00:16:44,916
Lin Shouyi is passable though.

344
00:16:44,958 --> 00:16:46,457
He can even drink with me.

345
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:49,999
You keep saying "Chen Ping'an."
Who is he?

346
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:50,957
Is he rich?

347
00:16:51,542 --> 00:16:52,542
Mother,

348
00:16:53,375 --> 00:16:54,374
character matters most

349
00:16:54,375 --> 00:16:56,832
when living life together.

350
00:16:57,042 --> 00:16:57,749
Just like Father.

351
00:16:58,042 --> 00:16:59,042
Though poor,

352
00:16:59,167 --> 00:17:00,957
he treats you so well.

353
00:17:01,250 --> 00:17:03,624
You should cherish that properly.

354
00:17:09,208 --> 00:17:09,666
Mother,

355
00:17:10,292 --> 00:17:11,624
I want to buy a box of rouge.

356
00:17:12,792 --> 00:17:14,749
Didn't you just buy one last year?

357
00:17:15,833 --> 00:17:16,957
You spend money so wastefully.

358
00:17:17,125 --> 00:17:18,707
Who will dare marry you in the future?

359
00:17:22,875 --> 00:17:23,707
This pot is expensive.

360
00:17:23,708 --> 00:17:24,249
Drink this first.

361
00:17:24,625 --> 00:17:27,041
Save the cheap one for the dinner table
later.

362
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:29,666
Then Mother won't call you a spendthrift.

363
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:34,832
I was used to staying at home before.

364
00:17:35,292 --> 00:17:36,749
I thought it was only natural

365
00:17:36,875 --> 00:17:38,666
for people to treat me well.

366
00:17:39,125 --> 00:17:41,791
But traveling with Chen Ping'an
opened my eyes.

367
00:17:42,167 --> 00:17:43,666
There are so many villains outside.

368
00:17:44,958 --> 00:17:46,166
Now I finally understand

369
00:17:46,292 --> 00:17:47,082
that a man like you,

370
00:17:47,250 --> 00:17:47,999
who treats Mother,

371
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:48,832
Sister, and me

372
00:17:48,958 --> 00:17:50,041
so well...

373
00:17:50,167 --> 00:17:51,167
is incredibly rare.

374
00:17:53,083 --> 00:17:54,083
Before...

375
00:17:54,167 --> 00:17:55,167
I'm sorry.

376
00:17:55,208 --> 00:17:55,916
Son,

377
00:17:56,083 --> 00:17:57,083
drink with your dad.

378
00:18:04,125 --> 00:18:05,125
This tastes awful.

379
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:08,666
Spend these next two days with Mother
and your sister.

380
00:18:08,875 --> 00:18:10,874
Tour the capital of Great Sai properly.

381
00:18:11,083 --> 00:18:13,124
Even if you can't afford nice things,

382
00:18:13,208 --> 00:18:14,624
it's good to look.

383
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:17,791
Later, when I succeed in my studies,

384
00:18:18,042 --> 00:18:18,582
I'll buy them for you.

385
00:18:18,583 --> 00:18:19,916
I promise I'll buy them.

386
00:18:20,167 --> 00:18:21,249
Don't worry.

387
00:18:21,375 --> 00:18:24,791
I'm doing very well at the academy.

388
00:18:25,208 --> 00:18:25,666
Really.

389
00:18:25,792 --> 00:18:27,749
My son knows how to care for his father now.

390
00:18:27,958 --> 00:18:28,958
I'm happy.

391
00:18:29,708 --> 00:18:31,874
Happier than breaking through a realm
with my fists.

392
00:18:32,458 --> 00:18:33,416
For all these years,

393
00:18:33,458 --> 00:18:35,874
I've been suppressing your talent
and bone structure.

394
00:18:36,375 --> 00:18:38,124
Now, you don't need to hide anymore.

395
00:18:38,375 --> 00:18:40,124
As for how far you ultimately go,

396
00:18:40,458 --> 00:18:41,666
that depends on you.

397
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:48,707
The Godly Sovereign cleaves the mountain,

398
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:49,832
creating a Cave Heaven.

399
00:18:51,875 --> 00:18:53,499
What kind of luck does Li Huai have?

400
00:18:53,708 --> 00:18:55,082
Sitting at home,

401
00:18:55,208 --> 00:18:56,707
fortune falls from the sky.

402
00:18:56,958 --> 00:18:58,541
Unlike you, you little money-loser.

403
00:18:59,625 --> 00:19:01,291
You can't even grasp the opportunities
handed to you.

404
00:19:03,708 --> 00:19:05,124
Yu Lu is different from you.

405
00:19:05,708 --> 00:19:06,874
Knowing something is impossible,

406
00:19:07,042 --> 00:19:09,457
he sought to use that old sword cultivator
as a whetstone to break through.

407
00:19:10,417 --> 00:19:12,457
He even managed to make Chen Ping'an
owe him a huge favor.

408
00:19:13,208 --> 00:19:14,791
Perhaps they might even become friends.

409
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:19,207
Since I publicly declared you
as my disciple,

410
00:19:19,875 --> 00:19:20,875
from now on,

411
00:19:23,833 --> 00:19:25,291
you are Xie Lingyue of the Lu Dynasty's

412
00:19:25,292 --> 00:19:27,416
premier immortal residence.

413
00:19:28,208 --> 00:19:29,208
Understand?

414
00:19:32,625 --> 00:19:33,749
Dragon Confining Nails.

415
00:19:34,042 --> 00:19:34,749
Thank you.

416
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:35,750
Thank you, Young Master.

417
00:19:37,625 --> 00:19:38,625
Remember this:

418
00:19:39,792 --> 00:19:40,999
From now on, you must fight desperately.

419
00:19:41,625 --> 00:19:43,041
Otherwise, go hang yourself somewhere.

420
00:19:49,583 --> 00:19:51,124
What should be done about her?

421
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,000
How about...

422
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:58,957
she becomes your mistress?

423
00:19:59,583 --> 00:20:00,957
I'm dying of laughter here.

424
00:20:04,833 --> 00:20:06,374
Thanks, thanks a lot.

425
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:08,457
Ambition soaring higher than the heavens,

426
00:20:08,458 --> 00:20:09,916
but fate thinner than paper.

427
00:20:10,417 --> 00:20:12,666
Unable to accept your current self...

428
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:15,124
Even if I remove the Dragon Confining Nails
for you,

429
00:20:15,125 --> 00:20:16,749
how far could you possibly walk?

430
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:21,791
Unlike my own Master,
whose heart-mind is pure,

431
00:20:21,792 --> 00:20:23,374
and whose Great Dao is full of promise.

432
00:20:23,398 --> 00:20:49,198
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

433
00:20:50,292 --> 00:20:51,374
Master.

434
00:20:58,500 --> 00:21:00,166
So, Master's Dao favors water...

435
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,082
allowing the Patriarchs of the Three Teachings

436
00:21:02,083 --> 00:21:03,624
to walk side-by-side in harmony.

437
00:21:04,125 --> 00:21:05,125
Master, please accept

438
00:21:05,458 --> 00:21:06,666
this bow from your student.

439
00:21:14,583 --> 00:21:15,041
Old Man,

440
00:21:15,458 --> 00:21:16,458
take a look at this treasure.

441
00:21:17,208 --> 00:21:18,291
The show is about to begin.

442
00:21:21,375 --> 00:21:22,582
Fairy Su...

443
00:21:22,875 --> 00:21:25,332
she is truly the apple of my eye.

444
00:21:25,917 --> 00:21:26,374
Just look at

445
00:21:26,708 --> 00:21:27,708
that figure,

446
00:21:27,875 --> 00:21:29,082
that temperament.

447
00:21:32,833 --> 00:21:33,999
Improper sights should not be seen.

448
00:21:35,833 --> 00:21:37,791
I'll trade her for just one
Snake Gallstone from you.

449
00:21:37,958 --> 00:21:38,958
Deal?

450
00:21:48,375 --> 00:21:49,375
It's snowing.

451
00:21:53,542 --> 00:21:56,166
Life is so meaningless.

452
00:22:13,208 --> 00:22:14,208
Master, Master!

453
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,457
A man and a woman have appeared
on the plank road.

454
00:22:16,917 --> 00:22:18,041
The man seems ordinary,

455
00:22:18,125 --> 00:22:19,749
but the woman... she has intense demonic
aura!

456
00:22:19,917 --> 00:22:20,999
What should we do?

457
00:22:25,208 --> 00:22:26,499
It's a Fox Demon.

458
00:22:26,917 --> 00:22:29,791
Fox demons in this world are known
for their stunning beauty.

459
00:22:30,042 --> 00:22:30,416
Father,

460
00:22:30,875 --> 00:22:32,832
I'll catch you a personal maid
to warm your bed.

461
00:22:32,833 --> 00:22:33,624
I'll catch you a personal maid
to warm your bed.

462
00:22:47,250 --> 00:22:48,250
Traveling in the snow...

463
00:22:48,667 --> 00:22:50,541
my attendant and I are truly exhausted.

464
00:22:50,875 --> 00:22:51,791
Young Master,

465
00:22:51,792 --> 00:22:52,999
might we rest for a moment?

466
00:22:56,375 --> 00:22:57,375
Granted.

467
00:23:03,708 --> 00:23:04,249
Old Man,

468
00:23:04,500 --> 00:23:05,124
why don't we...

469
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:06,500
Don't mess around, you two.

470
00:23:08,625 --> 00:23:10,874
My attendant released some demonic aura
earlier.

471
00:23:11,083 --> 00:23:11,749
Consider it a greeting.

472
00:23:11,750 --> 00:23:12,750
Consider it a greeting.

473
00:23:13,250 --> 00:23:14,250
Young Master, rest assured.

474
00:23:14,958 --> 00:23:15,958
We mean no harm.

475
00:23:17,083 --> 00:23:18,832
Your Martial Arts realm isn't high,

476
00:23:18,958 --> 00:23:20,332
but your Fist Intent is solid.

477
00:23:20,875 --> 00:23:21,875
Most impressive.

478
00:23:22,542 --> 00:23:23,542
Persist in this,

479
00:23:23,708 --> 00:23:24,957
and the Stopping Realm is within reach.

480
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,624
Thank you for your kind words, Sir.

481
00:23:32,042 --> 00:23:33,124
Do you know how to read this character?
"Learn."

482
00:23:34,833 --> 00:23:36,499
What a coincidence.

483
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:39,874
Young Master, your Bridge of Immortality
is broken—what a pity.

484
00:23:41,250 --> 00:23:42,250
To repair it...

485
00:23:42,708 --> 00:23:43,791
is harder than ascending to heaven.

486
00:23:44,708 --> 00:23:46,041
Better to find another path

487
00:23:46,333 --> 00:23:47,499
and rebuild one anew.

488
00:23:57,583 --> 00:23:58,583
Old Master Bai,

489
00:23:59,083 --> 00:24:01,207
you just met with the Literary Sage
not long ago,

490
00:24:01,625 --> 00:24:03,082
and now you encounter his disciple?

491
00:24:03,708 --> 00:24:04,791
Could it be...

492
00:24:05,042 --> 00:24:06,624
a scheme plotted by both Saints?

493
00:24:06,708 --> 00:24:08,207
I am merely traveling abroad
to ease my heart,

494
00:24:08,417 --> 00:24:09,417
free of desires and demands.

495
00:24:09,875 --> 00:24:11,541
If they still try to scheme against me,

496
00:24:11,875 --> 00:24:12,875
then I might as well

497
00:24:13,083 --> 00:24:15,166
attack that wall of theirs

498
00:24:15,458 --> 00:24:16,957
and change this world

499
00:24:17,583 --> 00:24:18,791
to have a new master.

500
00:24:19,958 --> 00:24:21,249
What difference would it make?

501
00:24:21,667 --> 00:24:23,041
Although you are of the Demon Race,

502
00:24:23,250 --> 00:24:25,707
you grew up in the Haoran World.

503
00:24:26,125 --> 00:24:28,041
Why are you so obsessed with meddling
in that conflict?

504
00:24:28,042 --> 00:24:29,541
The war between humans and demons,

505
00:24:29,875 --> 00:24:31,874
leaving two worlds devastated,

506
00:24:31,875 --> 00:24:33,124
nine out of ten homes empty.

507
00:24:33,333 --> 00:24:34,499
Is that fun?

508
00:24:34,500 --> 00:24:35,124
Old Master, spare my life!

509
00:24:35,125 --> 00:24:36,832
I don't think it's fun.

510
00:24:37,042 --> 00:24:38,791
Not interesting in the slightest.

511
00:24:41,667 --> 00:24:42,791
Qing Ying.

512
00:24:47,375 --> 00:24:48,291
There are some matters

513
00:24:48,917 --> 00:24:50,791
you cannot interfere with for now.

514
00:24:51,542 --> 00:24:54,166
If not for that tiny spark of karma
from back then,

515
00:24:54,375 --> 00:24:55,874
you would already be dead.

516
00:25:01,042 --> 00:25:02,291
A... a Great Demon!

517
00:25:02,458 --> 00:25:03,957
Holy shit, that's massive!

518
00:25:04,083 --> 00:25:05,249
Bigger than the sky!

519
00:25:05,583 --> 00:25:06,957
And she's just a servant?

520
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:08,916
Then isn't the man even more monstrous?

521
00:25:09,583 --> 00:25:10,583
Not necessarily.

522
00:25:10,833 --> 00:25:11,624
Our Old Master

523
00:25:11,625 --> 00:25:12,707
isn't as powerful as us.

524
00:25:13,292 --> 00:25:14,292
Oh, right.

525
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:15,624
Silly girl,

526
00:25:15,625 --> 00:25:16,625
learn to speak properly.

527
00:25:19,750 --> 00:25:21,332
Lu Chen.

528
00:25:21,708 --> 00:25:22,832
Imperial Edict.

529
00:25:31,125 --> 00:25:32,125
Old Master Bai,

530
00:25:32,292 --> 00:25:33,292
it's settled.

531
00:25:33,458 --> 00:25:35,249
Simply a matter of separate waters
not disturbing each other.

532
00:25:39,583 --> 00:25:40,583
Well now,

533
00:25:40,875 --> 00:25:42,582
when I sought you out, you hid.

534
00:25:43,167 --> 00:25:44,416
When I gave up hope,

535
00:25:44,875 --> 00:25:46,332
you came looking for me instead.

536
00:25:47,417 --> 00:25:50,624
I trouble Old Master Bai to keep an eye
on this young man.

537
00:25:51,208 --> 00:25:53,624
If the day comes when Humans and Demons
officially go to war,

538
00:25:54,000 --> 00:25:55,957
please, as a member of the Demon Race,

539
00:25:56,417 --> 00:25:57,417
after observing him,

540
00:25:57,958 --> 00:25:58,958
make your decision.

541
00:26:23,792 --> 00:26:24,832
Sword practice in a dream?

542
00:26:25,500 --> 00:26:26,582
Interesting.

543
00:26:27,167 --> 00:26:28,957
I heard you took a major tumble early on,

544
00:26:29,042 --> 00:26:30,207
and your cultivation has stagnated.

545
00:26:30,250 --> 00:26:30,749
What,

546
00:26:30,792 --> 00:26:33,416
you think forming a marriage alliance
with the Chen family of Yingyin

547
00:26:33,667 --> 00:26:34,916
will let you stage a comeback?

548
00:26:35,167 --> 00:26:36,167
Cao Jun,

549
00:26:36,375 --> 00:26:37,124
it is time for you to depart.

550
00:26:38,042 --> 00:26:39,042
Almost forgot to mention—

551
00:26:39,375 --> 00:26:40,499
my Cao family ancestors

552
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,457
also walked out from Mud Bottle Lane.

553
00:26:42,875 --> 00:26:44,666
I wonder if this return to my roots

554
00:26:44,875 --> 00:26:46,457
will stir up a slaughter,

